args: Botan is a Hinomotoan fighter who has\ncome to the Halidom to train.
One day, she sets out with the prince and his\nfriends in order to deal with some fiends...
Get ready for a pummeling, fiends! Yaaah!
Wow, Botan's incredible!\nThe fiends are flying everywhere!
Indeed. Though I fear her fervor\nbegets recklessness...
Huh? It dodged! Where the heck did it go?!
Don't worry about it. Now let's finish this!
I'm real sorry, everyone. I tried to help,\nbut I just ended up getting in the way.
I can't believe I let the enemy sneak up\nbehind me... Stupid!
You fight with a vigorous style,\nbut it is one that allows enemy\nmovements to lead you astray.
You're right. I need to be more aware\nof what they're doing.

Then you should work on refining your
skills in the areas of observation and
insight. This will help you predict where
an opponent will strike next.
Okay, sure. But HOW do I do that?
You want to know how to refine your\nobservation and insight?
Well, cleaning would help teach you to\nkeep an eye out for even the smallest\nbits of dirt and grime.
And hunting can teach you insight!\nYou've gotta predict where your target's\ngonna go next, right?
This is all real good advice. You gotta\nlearn to rely on all yer senses on the\nbattlefield, or else yer toast.
Speakin' of, I recommend bathin' in an\nicy stream. The cold'll freshen ya right up!
Cleaning, fishing, and icy bathing...\nGot it.
Hey, so will you guys help me?
Training! I'm going to do everything\nyou just threw at me!
Bwa ha ha! I love yer attitude, kid!\nBut yeah, we'd be glad to help.
I'm going to put everything I have into this.\nI won't let anyone down!
All right, that is one clean room!\nHow'd I do this time, Cleo?
Better. ...But I still see some dust here.
You must be mindful of every nook and\ncranny; a single missed spot is a blight\non the entire room.
A blight? Sheesh, man. Harsh.\nBut okay, I'll give it another go!
And when you can see the fish on\nthe water's surface...you strike!
You can't just watch and try to react.\nYou have to think about what the FISH\nis going to do next.
Got it. I'm gonna do it this time.\nTaaake...THIS!
Okay, so I don't mind the occasional\nchilly soak from time to time.\nOne might even call it refreshing.
But it is freakin' FREEZING here, Ranzal!\nI've got icicles comin' outta my nose!
Bwaaa ha ha! That means it's PERFECT!\nHere, watch me.
Hoooo BABY! The cold wind only makes\nit better! Now try it again!
Right! Clear my mind... Clear my mind...\nRaaargh!
And so, Botan worked tirelessly at her training.\nOne week later...
Urgh! This fiend's a strong one!
Take a rest, you two! I'll handle this.
Botan, no! It's still too much for
Hang on. Look how she's moving.
I see through EVERYTHING you do!\nHiyaaaaaah!
Uh oh. Now the fiend is hiding.\nI can't see where it went.
Sharpen your senses, focus on\nyour surroundings, aaand...there!\nIt's in the brush behind me!
You can't sneak up on me anymore!\nHiiii-YAH!
Nice, Botan! Looks like all of your\ntraining has really paid off.
I can't believe how much you improved\nin just a single week.
It's 'cause of how much everyone helped.
There's some truth to that, but I think\nyour hard work played a bigger part.
We saw you take action and push ahead\nin order to accomplish a goal. We could\nall stand to learn something from that.
Heh! Well, working myself to the bone\nIS one of my redeeming features.
But I'm gonna keep this up\nand get even stronger!
